-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zxb1665702710155.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zxb1665702710155.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zxb1665702710155.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zxb1665702710155\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Keyboard Translation Table\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Keyboard Translation Table is a Development Object that maps user input to <dfn class=\"term\">structure editor functions</dfn> recognized by Uniface.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zxb1665702710155__section_w1628ab1b5b1_w1629ab1b5_w1630ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zxb1665702710155__section_w1631ab1b5b3_w1632ab1b5_w1633ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d646519e59\">\n                     \n Characteristics\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ktt</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ijz1665702550775.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ijz1665702550775.html\" title=\"An Untyped Library is a Main Development Object that defines a collection of objects that may be of different types, and which can be reused or accessed by other objects during development or at runtime.\">Untyped Library</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyboardTableName</var>.ktt</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxb1665702710155__table_d10706e1_d10707e1_d10708e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ktt:<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyboardTableName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zxb1665702710155__section_w1634ab1b5b5_w1635ab1b5_w1636ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d646519e249\">\n                     \n Specialization\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zxb1665702710155__p_d96335e1_d96336e1_d96337e1\">Keyboard Translation Table specializes Development Object in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zxb1665702710155__li_d39041e1_d39042e1_d39043e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zxb1665702710155__p_d96338e1_d96339e1_d96340e1\">It has a Library as parent object. </p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zxb1665702710155__li_d39044e1_d39045e1_d39046e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zxb1665702710155__p_d96341e1_d96342e1_d96343e1\">It has no child development objects.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534664\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534664\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Keyboard Translation Table Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Keyboard Translation Table A Keyboard Translation Table is a Development Object that maps user input to structure editor functions recognized by Uniface. Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: ktt Main Development Object? No Part of: Untyped Library Contains: Property Generalization: Development Object Specializations: — Compilation Output: KeyboardTableName .ktt URI format: ktt: KeyboardTableName Specialization Keyboard Translation Table specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has a Library as parent object. It has no child development objects. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}